                        <interp inst="t18380618-name-114" type="given" value="DANIEL"></interp>DANIEL PAMPLET</persName>
                  </hi>. I am an officer. I took the prisoner and the lead now produced—I found in the room a knife and a pair of scissors with which the lead had been cut and prised—I fitted them to the marks on the lead.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner</hi>. My father is coachman to Dr. Birkbeck. I had a few words with my father, and he said I should not sleep in his house—I walked</p>
               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="183806180010"></xptr>
               <p>about and found this door open—I went in and slept, and the next morn<lb></lb>ing I was awoke by some persons knocking at the door—I opened it, and they gave me in charge—I do not know how the lead came there.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">MR. HEATH</hi>. I had seen the lead safe about a week before.</p>
               <p>(The prisoner received a good character.)</p>
